Bad Asses on the Bayou (also known as Bad Ass 3) is a 2015 action film starring Danny Trejo and Danny Glover, written and directed by Craig Moss. The film is the third part of the Bad Ass series.


== Plot synopsis ==
Frank Vega and Bernie Pope return, this time to Louisiana in an attempt to find a kidnapped friend.


